_sText:
My first map, just made with a few reference pictures.

Based loosely on the SoF2 map instant mincemeat.

This is supposed to be played on a server with the Deathmatch mod installed. Instant respawn weapon selction at beginning etc.

-Bobinator2000

Change log:
--------------
v1.0 -
Changed lighting in side rooms
Added grenades on walkways
Added two more spawn points to make it possible to have the maximum 64 players


v0.8 -
Added more spawn points - Now takes up to 62 players
Added a missing box
Added more ammo to the weapons on roof platform
Added nade pickups to the centre, side rooms and roof platform
Changed Sky texture


V0.7 -
Initial release
